sentences.english: Most importantly, this album has a stamp of Metallica written all over it.

sentences.english: Looking back, it was collective code ownership at its finest!
sentences.chinese: 现在回想起来，集体性的代码所有权非常有用。

sentences.english: Party B shall still have the ownership of the equipment until Party B is paid in full.
sentences.chinese: 甲方未付清全款前，设备的所有权仍归乙方所有。

sentences.chinese: 来料或来件的所有权仍属国外客户。

sentences.english: For the moment, Genuitec will retain ownership of Pulse.
Welcome to the ambiguous world of service ownership.
sentences.chinese: 欢迎来到服务所有权的混沌世界。

sentences.english: Structure of ownership is one of the most important fundaments and parts in the area of corporate governance research.

sentences.english: The great Chinese revolution was fundamentally about the ownership of land.
sentences.chinese: 从本质来说，中国的大革命即是土地所有权的革命。

sentences.english: Warwick presents Plantagenet's request to have his father's title passed on to him.
sentences.chinese: 华威介绍普朗塔的要求，有他父亲的所有权转交给他。

sentences.english: Support for multiple accounting standards and partial ownership consolidations.

sentences.english: The poor farmers do not have well - established claims to their land .

sentences.english: Allright, so today is the big day.
sentences.chinese: 所有权，因此，今天是伟大的一天。

sentences.english: He was a partial owner of the team, he owned part of this team until recently
sentences.chinese: 他有一部分球队的所有权，一直到最近都有。
